This directory is populated by build.bat which copies
../../forgetmenot/build/forgetmenot.exe → ./forgetmenot.exe
just before Go compiles the tray binary.

The embedded forgetmenot.exe is bundled inside forgetmenot-tray.exe via
Go's //go:embed directive (see runtime_embed.go) and extracted on
first launch to %LOCALAPPDATA%/ForgetMeNot/runtime/forgetmenot.exe.
